        This ticket gives you full access to the convention area and events on your selected day(s).<br />
        Accommodation is not included in this ticket.<br />
      </p>
    </FaqItem>
    <FaqItem question="What is included in my ticket?">
      <p><strong>Day(s) ticket</strong> includes:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Access to the convention area</li>
        <li>Access to all events on your selected day(s)</li>
      </ul>
      <p><strong>Residential ticket</strong> includes:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Access to the convention area</li>
        <li>Access to all events</li>
        <li>A bed at the Bedford Hotel</li>
        <li>Daily breakfast</li>
        <li>Daily room cleaning</li>
      </ul>
      <p><strong>Sponsor Pack</strong> includes your chosen ticket, plus:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>A convention T-shirt</li>
        <li>Custom lanyard</li>
        <li>Extra goodies</li>
        <li>Our eternal gratitude</li>
      </ul>
    </FaqItem>
  </Faq>
</Base>

<style lang="scss" is:global>
  @use '../styles/charter';
  @use '../styles/text-styles';

  #our_favorite_restaurants .accordion {
    margin-top: 48px;
    max-width: 500px;

    .accordion-item__header {
      @include text-styles.heading3;
      color: charter.$neutrals700;
    }

    .accordion-item__content {
      a {
        display: block;
      }
      @include text-styles.display3Regular;

      & + .accordion-item__header {
        border-top: solid 1px charter.$neutrals400;
      }
    }
  }

  #travel_info {
    display: grid;
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin-top: 48px;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 1px;
    background: charter.$neutrals400;

    > div {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 16px;
      padding: 48px 48px 60px 48px;
      background: charter.$neutrals200;

      @include text-styles.paragraphMediumRegular;
      color: charter.$neutrals600;

      h4 {
        @include text-styles.heading3;
        color: charter.$neutrals700;
      }

      ul {
        margin-left: 1em;
      }
    }
  }
</style>
